title: Tim Scott wants to strip China of its 'developing nation' status as part of trade platform
description: Sen. Tim Scott (R-SC) said China should be stripped of its “developing nation” status, an international designation that grants it special privileges and flexibility over the United States, as a means of ensuring the U.S. is not put at a disadvantage in trade.

title: Burbank mayor confronted by councilwoman about behavior: 'The line has been crossed'
description: Burbank, California, Mayor Konstantine Anthony faced sharp criticism from city council members and residents over a viral video on social media that showed him being spanked at a drag queen bingo event.
